OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny low cloud in the central
OL,6,Fbelt soon clearing during the morning
OL,7,Fwith all areas then having long spells
OL,8,Fof unbroken sunshine. Temperatures
OL,9,Fdown a bit, but still very warm,
OL,10,Fespecially inland. Light winds, with
OL,11,Fsome cooling sea breezes.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA fine warm sunny evening in
OL,14,Fall areas then a dry night with some
OL,15,Flong clear spells. Some patchy mist
OL,16,Faround dawn and perhaps clouding over
OL,17,Ftowards Mull.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
