OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FAnother dry day. There will
OL,6,Fbe some spells of sunshine. but a
OL,7,Fcloudier period is possible around the
OL,8,Fmiddle of the day.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FIt will
OL,11,Fbe a dry few days with variable cloud
OL,12,Fand some sunny spells. Mainly light
OL,13,Fwinds, and on the warm side.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
